<%- include('partials/head') %>
        <%- include('partials/header') %>

        <section class="whitebg">
            <div>
                <h6>Press any of the big buttons to instantly enter a room! OR you can pick out a specific room, create one, or play singleplayer on the "Rooms" tab above!</p>
            </div>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 nophone"></div>
                <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 butt-div">
                    <a href="/roombase?mode=casual" class="btn bigbutt btn-warning">CASUAL</a>
                    <p>No scores, just get as many words as you can every so often until the word changes. Good to get started or just chill!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 nophone"></div>
                <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 butt-div">
                    <a href="/roombase?mode=time_attack" class="btn bigbutt btn-danger">TIME ATTACK</a>
                    <p>A race against the clock! Whoever can get the most words within the time limit wins.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 nophone"></div>
                <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 butt-div">
                    <a href="/roombase?mode=first_to_3" class="btn bigbutt btn-primary">1ST 2 3</a>
                    <p>A true competition, a race for who can find enough words. The first to reach the designated amount of words wins.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="graybg">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-6">
                    <h3>What is Matrioska?</h3>
                    <p>Matrioska is a fast-paced word game where your goal is to find smaller, hidden words inside a main "Master Word". The longer the hidden word you find, the more points you score. Keep peeling the letters to climb the ranks!</p>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-6">
                    <h3>Play with Friends!</h3>
                    <p>You don't have to play alone. Join public lobbies or create private rooms to challenge your friends in real-time. Choose your favorite game mode, test your vocabulary, and see who dominates the global leaderboard!</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="whitebg tutorial">
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-12 text-center mb-5">
                    <h2 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-3">HOW TO PLAY</h2>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-4">
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <div class="bg-warning rounded-circle d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mx-auto mb-3" style="width: 80px; height: 80px;">
                            <span class="fs-3 fw-bold">1</span>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Get the Master Word</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted">Every round starts with a long "Master Word". Your mission is to look closely at its letters and find hidden meanings.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-4">
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <div class="bg-danger rounded-circle d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mx-auto mb-3" style="width: 80px; height: 80px;">
                            <span class="fs-3 fw-bold">2</span>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Peel the Layers</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted">Find smaller words hidden inside the main word. Golden Rule: The letters must appear in the exact direct or indirect sequence.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-12 col-lg-4">
                    <div class="text-center">
                        <div class="bg-primary rounded-circle d-inline-flex align-items-center justify-content-center mx-auto mb-3" style="width: 80px; height: 80px;">
                            <span class="fs-3 fw-bold">3</span>
                        </div>
                        <h4 class="fw-bold mb-3">Score Big</h4>
                        <p class="text-muted">Submit your words before the timer runs out. The more layers you uncover, or the longer the hidden word is, the more points you earn!</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                
                <div class="col-12 text-center mt-5">
                    <h2 class="display-4 fw-bold mb-3">READY TO PLAY?</h2>
                    <p class="lead mb-4">Join an active lobby or create your own custom game.</p>
                    <a href="/roomlist" class="btn btn-success btn-lg bigbutt">ROOMS</a>
                </div>
            </div>

            
        </section>



        <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    </div>


    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.8/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-FKyoEForCGlyvwx9Hj09JcYn3nv7wiPVlz7YYwJrWVcXK/BmnVDxM+D2scQbITxI" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
</body>
</html>
